sub_title: Project & Change Management Consultant ☆Helping Individuals & Businesses Change☆
summary:
I am a project and change management professional, with 7+ years of experience in project management. I am APMG Change Management Practitioner certified, currently following Agile Change Agent Course with APMG International.

If you'd like to have a discussion about change, feel free to reach out to me here in LinkedIn, or at katsiaryna.karliuk@gmail.com
